Package: absCopyNumber
Type: Package
Title: Tumor Purity, Ploidy and Absolute Copy Number Estimation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Shixiang", "Wang", email = "w_shixiang@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9855-7357")),
            person("Bao", "Lei", email = "lebao@ucsd.edu", role="aut")) 
Maintainer: Shixiang Wang <w_shixiang@163.com>
URL: https://github.com/ShixiangWang/AbsoluteCopyNumber
BugReports: https://github.com/ShixiangWang/AbsoluteCopyNumber/issues
Description: Estimate tumor purity, ploidy and absolute copy numbers from NGS (WGS, WES, Target Sequencing) 
             and Microarray (SNP, aCGH etc.) data, based on statistical method from paper 
             "AbsCN-seq: a statistical method to estimate tumor purity, ploidy and absolute copy numbers 
             from next-generation sequencing data".
Depends: R (>= 2.13.0)
Imports: graphics, stats, utils
